Login:
Refugee-Generate unique id based on the location using a separate web portal
NGO Register

To Track and to make sure that refugees are not clustered in one place there will be soft boundary for each region and if number of refugees in a region exceed a new area will be allocated along with a new id

Refugee side Interface consist of following feature:
1) See nearby shelters for aid such as food, shelter, health
2) Raise an issue regarding the shelters or any problem faced
3) Register/attend donation drive or events hosted by NGO(Note: there will be limit on number of such events a refugee can attend and also a cooldown period after attending specified number of events)
4) There will be navigation system to locate all specified things
5) Providing multilingual support

NGO side:
1) Register
2) List events
3) receive feedback
